    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in truly breathtaking condition, looking and driving exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free from any chips, scratches, or swirl marks, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection; the premium leather seats show zero signs of wear or bolster compression, the dashboard is pristine, and it still retains that distinctive new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is faultless, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using only genuine OEM parts. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. This is not merely a well-kept used car; it is a collector-grade example intended for the most discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection. Sale includes all original keys, factory manuals, and a documented maintenance binder.",
